Source: poly-app-kodi
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: OpenPolycom <apt@openpolycom.cc>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: poly-app-kodi
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, kodi, fonts-noto-core, alsa-utils
Recommends: ffmpeg
Description: Application: Kodi media player (weston client)
 Metapackage for the media-player application: Kodi running fullscreen as
 the kiosk's Wayland client (KIOSK_ENGINE=kodi in kiosk-launch). Per-board
 pieces (the C60 portrait UI and its ALSA routing) come from
 poly-kodi-skin-c60portrait. Board-agnostic: runs on any
 Polycom panel this project supports.
